text: This is the only appropiate thing for DCN's final tweet. Thank you, everyone! https://t.co/ZEeoNpN3ej
@DarrenCriss Good luck with everything, buddy! I ❤ you!
But it's time to take a step back, and enjoy things as a regular fan. So make no mistake, I'm still and forever will be a Darren Criss fan.
For me, it's an experience that will never be duplicated. I'm so grateful for everything, good AND bad.
And today marks the end of the site. A project very dear to my heart, that for 4 years took over my life.
2 days ago marked the 4th anniversary of DCN.
